dataIdInfo.idAbs: The dataset represents communes (admin level 3) of Mali.

Consts.useLimit: See the COD/FOD Registry Terms of Use. This does not replace any terms of use information provided with the dataset.

dataLineage.statement:
Admin 3 shapefile was downloaded from the OCHA COD Registry by ITOS and was analyzed for errors. Those errors were corrected. The layer was then updated with new name spellings, p-codes and attribution from a master list provided by the IMO, "New_Mali_admin_pcode_20150330.xlsx". It was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS:
1. Created and populated a reference name field. 2. Fixed geometry errors concerning multi-part polygons and overlaps. 3. Two records had their names modified: ʺSIKASSO Communeʺ was changed to proper case; period removed from name ʺFarakou Massa.ʺ 4. As instructed by the IMO, Admin3 unit "Sasalbe" has changed Admin2 attribution from "Tenenkou" to "Mopti". Admin3 p-codes for units in "Tenenkou" and "Mopti" have been updated to reflect this change.
